OL,3,CReform complains to BBC about
OL,4,CCaerphilly by-election debate 'plant'
OL,6,FReform UK has complained to the BBC
OL,7,Fafter it emerged that a prominent
OL,8,Faudience member at a by-election
OL,9,Fdebate is running as a Plaid Cymru
OL,10,Fcandidate.
OL,12,FVoters in Caerphilly went to the polls
OL,13,Fafter the sudden death of Labour
OL,14,FSenedd Member Hefin David last year.
OL,16,FBBC Wales held a television debate
OL,17,Fwith six of the candidates called Your
OL,18,FVoice, Your Vote, in the lead-up to
OL,19,Fpolling day.
