OL,4,CCaerphilly by-election debate 'plant'
OL,6,FNigel Farage's party had pledged to
OL,7,F"throw everything" at its campaign for
OL,8,Fthe seat, which Labour had held since
OL,9,Fthe Senedd was established in 1999.
OL,11,FPlaid has since announced the audience
OL,12,Fmember, Alison Vyas, as a community
OL,13,Fcouncil candidate in Caerphilly.
OL,15,FA Facebook post announcing her
OL,16,Fcandidacy described her as a "proud
OL,17,FValleys woman" who "brings the
OL,18,Fstrength, warmth, and community spirit
OL,19,Fshe grew up with".
