OL,3,CReform complains to BBC about
OL,4,CCaerphilly by-election debate 'plant'
OL,6,FMr Farage said: "Trust in the BBC has
OL,7,Fbeen shaken by scandals in recent
OL,8,Fyears, from Huw Edwards to the
OL,9,Fselective editing of a clip of
OL,10,FPresident Trump.
OL,12,F"Now, this revelation will be the
OL,13,Ffinal straw for many people in Wales.
OL,15,F"How can there be any confidence that
OL,16,FReform will get a fair and balanced
OL,17,Fhearing when this is the kind of thing
OL,18,Fthat happens at key election debates?"
